http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gauff\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"a backhand\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"the baseline\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"the linesperson\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"her racket\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the chair umpire, Jaume Campistol, took a different view, overruling the original decision before awarding the point to Vekic, putting the 28-year-old just two games away from victory.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chair umpire\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"Jaume Campistol\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"a different view\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"the original decision\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"Vekic\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 864}, {\"ngram\": \"the 28-year-old just two games\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A heated discussion then ensued between Gauff and Campistol, which resulted in the world number two breaking down in tears and accusing the officials of 'cheating' her out of a potential victory.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A heated discussion\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"Gauff\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"Campistol\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"the world number\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"a potential victory\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Campistol held firm on his decision and Vekic - a semi-finalist at Wimbledon earlier this summer - went on to wrap up the win in emphatic fashion to secure a place in the quarter-finals.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Campistol\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"firm\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"Vekic\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"a semi\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"finalist\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"emphatic fashion\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarter-finals\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GAUFF 'I was going back to hit the ball and he called it out before I hit it.'\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UMPIRE 'You understand that I have to take a decision and in this case\\u2026' GAUFF 'But you have to be sure\\u2026' UMPIRE 'I am 100 per cent sure in this case.'\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GAUFF 'You are not, you just said maybe I am wrong!'\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"UMPIRE 'Based on your reaction I might be wrong.'\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your reaction\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GAUFF 'I never argue these calls but he called it out before I hit the ball.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these calls\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It always happens to me on this court!\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this court\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Call the supervisor.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the supervisor\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It always happens to me, every time.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You understand that I always have to advocate for myself, all the time.\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am getting cheated in this game.\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this game\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You guys are not fair to me.'\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"You guys\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Croatian No.13 seed Vekic saw off Italy's Lucia Bronzetti and Canada's Bianca Andreescu to secure her place in the third round against Gauff.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998980852122, \"rank\": 7.076810497884765e-08, \"text\": \"Croatian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999744832379792, \"rank\": 2.0465952635274326e-05, \"